msg: Only after we flush the ra_svn send buffer can we be sure that
the receiver has a chance to answer. Therefore, check_for_error
should not be a no-op the next time it is called.
While at it, fix a few "unused function" compiler warnings.
(svn_ra_svn_flush): set the flag that enables check_for_error
